contents: Move the scissors towards the space between the cassette and the knife~~~

Move the airplane one square closer to the barrel, keeping it in the top row~~~

Move the barrel down so that it is above the sunglasses~~~ Do not move the sunglasses~~~
Move the saxophone up so it remains in the same column, but is in the same row as the barrel~~~

Move the wrench to be directly next to the "A" block and in the top row~~~
Move the "B" block one square away from the edge while remaining in the same row~~~
Move the blue "B" block one square towards the binoculars, while keeping it in the same row~~~
